Data tables, 2021 Census About the 2021 Census Data tables: This series of cross-tabulations will present a portrait of Canada based on the various census topics. They will range in complexity and will be available for various levels of geography. A number of the tabulations will be available on each official day of release for each topic, while others will follow several months later. Content varies from: A simple overview of the country Simple to more complex cross-tabulations Current and previous census data.
